imentioned earlier has led to the creation of at least two gopher		gopher.black	70
iclients I know of that match that gopher purist philosophy. We		gopher.black	70
ialso have VF-1, a lovely python client that inspired a fork for		gopher.black	70
ioffline browsing of the whole small internet, and another fork for		gopher.black	70
igemini. Bombadillo is fun, and there's my most recent favorite,		gopher.black	70
iphetch. Lots of options all with better features and better		gopher.black	70
ihandling of gopherspace.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iFor me, the benifits of being able to link within the documents		gopher.black	70
ioutweighs the negatives. The format is subverted with my tooling,		gopher.black	70
iand I don't feel the need to lower my gopher content to an ancient		gopher.black	70
